      "text": "TRADE-OFFS\n\nКомпромиссы — ключевое\nв ML System Design.\n\n• Accuracy vs Latency\n• Precision vs Recall\n• Freshness vs Cost\n• Complexity vs Maint.\n• Memory vs Speed\n• Online vs Offline\n• Batch vs Real-time",
      "fontSize": 12,
